relation: Darrow5 - #23 As strange as it seems, Groucho's still around after all these years. What a favorable fellow.

Darrow5 - #24 Jeff's knowledge of RPGs certainly helps in most cases. However, for those who want to collect all of the treasure, often times taking the furthest route first is not the best idea. Sometimes the best treasure is in the closest hole, while the plot advances at the last hole. Oh, cruel game developers!
Darrow5 - #25 With a crash and a bang, Thunder and Storm....wait, nevermind. Apparently they have something else in mind...

Darrow5 - #26 Thunder and Storm whip out their Manzai-like comedy act, which fails to impress. Cultural differences between Dalaamese Sanctuary enemies and Eagleland citizens are just too great, it seems.
Darrow5 - #27 Being a comedian is tough. It's even tougher when you're actually meant to be a henchman for an evil alien.
